---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="About" description="About Stratos — a Sun Fast 3300 racing program based at Cedar Point Yacht Club.">
  <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
    <h1>About Stratos</h1>

    <h2>The Boat</h2>
    <table>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td><strong>Design</strong></td><td>Sun Fast 3300</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Sail number</strong></td><td>15833</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Hull</strong></td><td>#76, built 2022</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>ORC rating</strong></td><td>537.3</td></tr>
        <tr><td><strong>Home port</strong></td><td>Cedar Point Yacht Club, Westport CT</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>The Program</h2>
    <p>
      <em>Stratos</em> campaigns primarily single-handed and double-handed offshore distance racing on the US Northeast Coast.
      The offshore program centers on the Bermuda Race, Annapolis to Newport, Bermuda 1-2, Block Island Race, and the Vineyard Race.
      Crewed inshore racing runs out of Cedar Point Yacht Club and neighboring clubs on Long Island Sound.
    </p>

    <h2>Sails</h2>
    <p>North Sails and Evolution Sails inventory includes a J0 and asymmetrical spinnakers: A1.5, A2, A3, A4.</p>

    <h2>Owner / Driver</h2>
  </div>

  <!-- Owner section: photo + bio side by side, outside prose to control layout -->
  <div class="not-prose mt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 items-start max-w-none">
    <div class="shrink-0">
      <img
        src="/images/marcus.jpg"
        alt="Marcus Wunderlich"
        class="w-56 rounded object-cover"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="prose prose-gray">
      <p>
        Marcus Wunderlich has been racing sailboats for over 15 years across a wide range of one-design
        and offshore classes. His background includes competitive campaigns on the J/105, J/70, VX One,
        Melges 15, and ILCA 7, with participation in numerous local, regional, and national regattas
        throughout his career.
      </p>
      <p>
        <em>Stratos</em> represents his move into offshore and shorthanded distance racing. Based at
        Cedar Point Yacht Club in Westport, CT, Marcus campaigns the Sun Fast 3300 primarily
        single- and double-handed on the US Northeast Coast.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
